snippet.title: PARTNERS IN CRIME! GULLY TRAILER REACTION (2021)
snippet.description:
PARTNERS IN CRIME! GULLY TRAILER REACTION (2021)
#GULLY #GULLYMOVIE #TRIBECA

This video is my reaction to the Official trailer of GULLY!
In Depth analysis and discussion of potential plot leaks, hidden easter eggs, and a review of what the trailer has shown us! There is a lot of information in this trailer!! Let me know what you think! Will this movie be GOOD? GULLY MOVIE
